                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6550" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1033</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9279 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从局中云雀到觉醒突围——HC直播电商企业的税筹历险记</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Rectification After Being Deceived——The Tax Financing Adventure of HC Live Broadcast E-commerce Enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑红霞，李晓悦，徐佳平</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛西海岸海创文化科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">直播电商；偷逃税款；税务筹划；电商主播；税务中介机构；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Live E-commerce; Tax Evasion; Tax Planning; Live streaming host; Tax intermediary</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">直播电商作为新媒体时代衍生出的一种新兴业态，近两年在政策滋养和疫情推动下发展迅猛，但行业在野蛮生长的同时也暴露出许多亟待解决的规范性问题，其中以偷逃税款、虚假宣传、产品质量低劣、消费维权困难等尤为突出。本案例讲述了一家发展形势大好的网红孵化机构——HC文化科技公司，因其签约的头号主播与公司合作的第三方税务筹划机构合谋进行偷逃税，从而使得公司陷入涉税困境。公司创始人在接到税务机关约谈通知后及时采取措施，在专业机构的帮助下进行彻底的自查、整改，使内部涉税风险得以控制，最终公司转危为安。本案例旨在引导学生了解当前直播电商行业中各主体涉税特点与税收征管难点的同时，让学生认识税务筹划与偷逃税的本质区别，明确纳税主体、第三方涉税服务机构与税务机关的三方责任，进一步引起学生对优化直播电商行业相关税制的思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As an emerging business form derived from the new media era, live e-commerce has developed rapidly in the past two years under the support of policies and the promotion of the epidemic. However, while the industry is growing wildly, it also exposes many normative problems that need to be solved urgently. Among them, tax evasion This is particularly the case for money, false propaganda, poor product quality, and difficulties in safeguarding consumer rights. This case tells about a well-developed Internet celebrity incubator, HC Technology and Culture Company, because its contracted number one anchor and a third-party tax planning agency cooperating with the company conspired to evade tax, thus putting the company in a tax-related predicament. The founder of the company took timely measures after receiving the notice of the interview from the tax authority, and conducted a thorough self-examination and rectification with the help of professional institutions, so that the internal tax-related risks could be controlled, and the company finally turned the corner. The purpose of this case is to guide students to understand the tax-related characteristics and difficulties of tax collection and management of various entities in the current live broadcast e-commerce industry, and at the same time, let students understand the essential difference between tax planning and tax evasion, and clarify the taxpayers, third-party tax-related service agencies and tax authorities. The tripartite responsibility of the live broadcast further aroused students&#39; thinking on optimizing the relevant tax system of the live broadcast e-commerce industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《税收筹划》、《税收理论与实务》、《企业税收风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息不对称理论；税务中介的服务规范与违规责任；节税、避税、税务筹划和偷逃税定义；三种类型的税务筹划税务风险管理理论；税收代理理论；利益相关者理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
